<exercise>
  <title>C4 - Homogeneous second-order linear IVP (ver. 31)</title>
  <statement>
    <p>Find the solution to the given IVP.</p>
    <me>y''+3y'-4y = 0 \hspace{1em} y(0) = 3 , y'(0) = 8</me>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>y= -e^{\left(-4 \, t\right)} + 4 \, e^{t}</me>
  </answer>
</exercise>
